data.title: Clariant releases Integrated Report 2025, offering comprehensive overview of financial and non-financial performance.
data.description: Clariant recently unveiled its Integrated Report 2025, offering a detailed summary of the company's financial and non-financial achievements. This report is designed to give stakeholders a deep understanding of Clariant's performance across various metrics. The report covers a wide range of areas including revenue figures, profit margins, sustainability initiatives, and overall strategic direction. It aims to provide transparency and accountability to investors, employees, and the general public regarding Clariant's operations and future goals.

data.title: EfTEN Real Estate Fund AS approved audited 2025 annual report with unchanged financial results from preliminary report.
data.description: EfTEN Real Estate Fund AS has announced that its Supervisory Board has given approval to the audited annual report for the year 2025. The report will be presented for final approval at the upcoming General Meeting of Shareholders. The financial results outlined in the audited report remain consistent with the preliminary financial results released on January 29, 2026. The Fund's numbers have not been altered, indicating stability and accuracy in its financial reporting process.

data.title: "BEPPU PROJECT installs new artwork "space II" by art team "me" in ALTERNATIVE-STATE project for Beppu experience."
data.description: BEPPU, Japan - BEPPU PROJECT, a nonprofit organization in Beppu City, Oita Prefecture, southwestern Japan, unveiled the latest artwork "space II" by the art team "me" in "ALTERNATIVE-STATE." This project, initiated in 2022, aims to elevate the city's hot springs experience. The installation marks a new addition to the ongoing project, showcasing innovative art in the region.
